Cash is a medium of exchange, a debt note for a promise of payment. You are paid Cash as a store of value for the time and services provided. Inflating the money supply is theft; it steals from your efforts and store of wealth by diluting the supply and reducing its purchasing power. The value of assets goes up proportionately to the debasement of the dollar. Currency debasement creates a hidden tax on inflationary gains while devaluing debts. CPI is misleading from substitutes and cheats those on Social Security and fixed incomes. Empires that debase their currency, cheat their populous, rob future generations, and eventually fail. 
We need sound money. #Bitcoin
